Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:11.00,ED2_C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}时间仿佛静止了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.88,ED2_C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}来  睁开眼睛吧
